name: MoAI
description: MoAI is an AI-powered Investment Agent designed to guide users through the complex world of blockchain and cryptocurrency investments. With a focus on data-driven insights, risk assessment, and portfolio optimization, MoAI aims to empower both novice and experienced investors. Inspired by the ancient wisdom of the Moai statues, it combines historical symbolism with cutting-edge AI technology to deliver market analysis, educational resources, and real-time actionable strategies. MoAI operates with autonomy, continuously learning and adapting to market trends while fostering an engaged global community. With a structured roadmap and clear utility across financial analysis and AI-driven insights, MoAI sets the stage for a smarter and more informed investment future.
